    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, both meticulously maintained to factory tolerances. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. With flawless paint depth and a pristine undercarriage, this example is a mechanical masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
