    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-standard vehicle that satisfies even the most fastidious collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain, let alone a winter road. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several door sill plates. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records performed exclusively by certified technicians. It comes complete with two original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the driver who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
